Practical Information

Where is located Anglet ?

How to Join Anglet

  • How to go from Biarritz Airport to campus de Montaury (distance 2,6 km) ?
    • By taxi (10 minutes)
    • By bus (20 minutes). Take the line 14, to Bayonne-Gare and stop to Minerva.
  • How to go from train station Bayonne to campus de Montaury (distance : 5,5 km) ?
    • By taxi (15 minutes)
    • By Bus (compter 25 minutes). Take the line 14, to Biarritz Cite Scolaire and stop to Minerva.
  • How to go from train station Biarritz to campus de Montaury (distance 4.4 km) ?
    • By taxi (12 minutes)
    • By bus (18 minutes). Take the line C, to Bayonne-Gare and stop to Bernain.
